{"tid":2132334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要接受  初選、上屆區選就已經係議會 End Game","createTime":"2020-07-30T10:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T12:13:09.000Z","uid":89160,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"298fda3baa9b8057324b242742d66bc8d3cf4967","tid":2132334,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"orange\">有人話杯葛，有人話 Plan B，但點解大家唔先珍惜 60 萬人既選擇？</span></strong><br />\n60萬人已經係一個正常、合法選舉需要既票數，雖然無公權力，但有公信力<br />\n<br />\n就算你杯葛立會選舉又好，Plan B 又好，都係一個受操控既選舉，有公權力而欠公信力<br />\n依家應該去諗點樣確立「初選勝選人」及或「現任民選區議員」既認受性<br />\n<br />\n我唔阻止大家去點應對 DQ ，繼續玩又好，唔玩又好，唔應該為呢件事嘈<br />\n但大家要認清現實，初選、上屆區選就已經係議會 End Game<br />\n<br />\n利申：<strong><span class=\"orange\">首先反對港獨，反對任何分裂國家行為，沒有共產黨就沒有新中國</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f4ea84278b5fff3a9a257ad3abc0fbd7c25f3468","tid":2132334,"uid":89160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:21:14.000Z","msg":"唔好亂，大家應該預計到架，係咪"},{"pid":"f7a8220eff11d2c864372f5a903f1a681db5d350","tid":2132334,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aa45fd0d088e7b86393ad2b1b91aa33bfa0100c","tid":2132334,"uid":199893,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:22:29.000Z","msg":"最多咪End咗議會戰線<br />\n唔係end game"},{"pid":"7ea4c1e980222081f47f4c13132ca7f1f3e60675","tid":2132334,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"orange\">唔好畀風向吹到互咬，事實初選大家已經作左決擇<br />\n毋須要再嘈</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4706616073262db977ff9f6017b21888a8a9b7df","tid":2132334,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5543c7b28035270e24637cf1b27f57e56aa52a0c","tid":2132334,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aa45fd0d088e7b86393ad2b1b91aa33bfa0100c","tid